#预测及绘图
fg,ax=plt.subplots(30,2,figsize=(8,60))

for i in range(1,31):
    img=cv.imread(f'{i}.jpg')
    img1=cv.resize(img,(32,32),interpolation=cv.INTER_NEAREST)
    knn.predict([img1.ravel()])
    
    ax[i-1,0].imshow(img)
    ax[i-1,1].set_title(str(knn.predict([img1.ravel()])))
    ax[i-1,1].imshow(img1)
